<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta name="description" content="PDF Blender (Merger) is a web based app for merging PDF files."/>
    <title>PDF Blender - Merge PDF files</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true"/>
</head>
<body>
